name: Elon Drip Musk
description: ELON MUSK. You have changed the world, the crypto market and the people. We in the community, love you a lot and we just wish that we get to meet you some day. You are the best ! If you ever get to read this (I know you won't), just know that we are glad about all the good you've done. Wish you all the best for the rest of your life.
